Anders adopts nearly every abandoned Pokémon he sees (ser pounce a lot is one of these Pokémon of course)

Dorian has an alolan Meowth cause they have the same energies

summary: (slightly random lol) do you think Alain would scold/punish mairin for cursing or would he not care?
question: (slightly random lol) do you think Alain would scold/punish mairin for cursing or would he not care?
answer:
I can think of some fun ideas about this:

  • When they are young, I see Alain surprised to hear Mairin say bad words, and I mean strong words. Maybe it’s because he still sees her as an innocent child.
  • As they grow up, he has become accustomed, especially because Mairin does not like to be told that she “can’t say or do something” and would do it more often just to annoy him.
  • Afterwards it would be like an internal joke, Mairin says a rudeness and he scolds her as a joke. How the “Take care of your language” of Capitan America in the MCU.

PS: I like these random questions about OTP, they make me happy to think about them.
PD 2: Sorry for my English.
